             were indicted for <rs id="t18211205-117-off723" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18211205-117-off723" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211205-117-off723" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18211205-117-cd724" type="crimeDate">3d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211205-117-off723 t18211205-117-cd724"></join>, one snuff box, value 1 l., and one pocket-book, value 1 s., the goods of <rs id="t18211205-117-viclabel725" type="occupation">Sir</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211205-117-victim1291 t18211205-117-viclabel725"></join> 
                  
                     
